metadata.name: Please return Woodie #6807
metadata.description:
Woodie #6807 was stolen in a phishing scam on March 19, 2023. As an early Woodies collector & community member, this NFT is very meaningful to me & I'd like to recover it.

Happy to pay you back your cost + a reward (or a literal "token" of my appreciation - something from my collection) for its safe return. Please dm me on Twitter @justthego to hash out the details. Thank you!
